Class MenuEntity

Object
PersistenceManager
MenuEntity
public class MenuEntity extends PersistenceManager
This is the parent object for all alacarte and package entities contains array list of all alacarte items and array list of all packages
Since:
2021-11-11
Version:
0.1.0
Author:
